name: AKAucklandBuses
0:
”Alexa, launch A. K. Buses”
”Add stop 4229 to my favorites”
”What buses are departing at 7 A.M. tomorrow?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: a. k. buses
des:
Add your local four-digit Auckland Transport bus stop or stops as favorites. Once they are saved, you can ask for the bus schedule without telling me the stop number. 

You can ask things like "When is the next bus?" or "What buses are there at 9 A.M. tomorrow?".
